---
<section id="scout" class="scout-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="scout-card">
      <div class="scout-content">
        <span class="eyebrow">База актеров</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Хочешь в кино?</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Мы постоянно ищем новые лица для наших проектов и партнерских кастингов.
          Попади в закрытую базу агентства «Эмоция» сегодня.
        </p>
        
        <ul class="scout-benefits">
          <li>
            <span class="check-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Приоритет на кастингах</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Профессиональное портфолио</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="check-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Рассылка закрытых проб</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="scout-actions">
          <a href="#contacts" class="btn btn-primary glow-effect">
            Подать анкету
          </a>
          <span class="scout-note">Это бесплатно для учеников студии</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="scout-visual">
         <!-- Abstract decorative elements asking for attention -->
         <div class="neon-circle"></div>
         <div class="camera-icon">🎥</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .scout-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background-color: #000;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
  }

  /* Main Card */
  .scout-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #18181b 0%, #09090b 100%);
    border: 1px solid #27272a;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px -10px rgba(147, 51, 234, 0.15); /* purple shadow */
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .scout-card {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }

  /* Content Side */
  .scout-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #c084fc; /* purple-400 */
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #a1a1aa; /* zinc-400 */
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .scout-benefits {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .scout-benefits li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #e4e4e7; /* zinc-200 */
  }

  .check-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    background: rgba(147, 51, 234, 0.2);
    color: #c084fc;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Actions */
  .scout-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: #9333ea;
    color: white;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #7e22ce;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .glow-effect {
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(162, 89, 255, 0.4);
  }

  .scout-note {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #71717a; /* zinc-500 */
  }

  /* Visual Side (Decorative) */
  .scout-visual {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 40%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .scout-visual {
      display: block;
    }
  }

  .neon-circle {
    position: absolute;
    right: -20%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147, 51, 234, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(40px);
  }

  .camera-icon {
    position: absolute;
    right: 15%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(-15deg);
    font-size: 8rem;
    opacity: 0.1;
    filter: grayscale(1);
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
  }

  .scout-card:hover .camera-icon {
    transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(0deg) scale(1.1);
    opacity: 0.2;
    filter: grayscale(0);
  }
</style>
